Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:13.77,def2,..BUNTA..,0,0,0,,You used to be a wild street\Nracer when you were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:16.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの頃とは時代が違うんだ
