Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:42.46,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,暗い道の先にぼんやりにじむ明かり
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.78,0:25:46.43,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,It's the silence like a silent film.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.88,0:25:46.40,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,If the tires strike a silent wind
